casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellee, v. Zych, Appellant.

[Cite as State v. Zych (1996), 74 Ohio St.3d 582.]

(No. 95-1959 Submitted January 9, 1996 Decided February 21, 1996.) Donald W. White, Clermont County Prosecuting Attorney, and David H. Hoffmann, Assistant Prosecuting Attorney, for appellee. Jeffrey A Zych, pro se. Per Curiam.

We affirm the decision of the court of appeals for the reasons stated in its entry.

Judgment affirmed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., concur.
